Installing from sources

   1. Unpack Infusion source package
   2. Go to Infusion folder and type "phpize && ./configure && make && make install"
   3. Make sure you have extension=infusion.so in your php.ini

Compiling Sysload into PHP

   1. Unpack Infusion source package to $PHP_SOURCE_DIR/ext/infusion
   2. In php source root directory run commands: "rm configure && ./buildconf --force"
   3. Configure PHP with command "./configure --with-infusion"
   4. Run make && make install

